format/configuration/README.md
     1вҶ’# Configuration
     2вҶ’
     3вҶ’This section details the configuration options available in the ***book.toml***:
     4вҶ’- **[General]** configuration including the `book`, `rust`, `build` sections
     5вҶ’- **[Preprocessor]** configuration for default and custom book preprocessors
     6вҶ’- **[Renderer]** configuration for the HTML, Markdown and custom renderers
     7вҶ’- **[Environment Variable]** configuration for overriding configuration options in your environment
     8вҶ’
     9вҶ’[General]: general.md
    10вҶ’[Preprocessor]: preprocessors.md
    11вҶ’[Renderer]: renderers.md
    12вҶ’[Environment Variable]: environment-variables.md
